comments: Schofield (ORL) commits a take foul on Stevens (CLE).  After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the contact did not meet the criteria for a clear path foul and a common foul was assessed.
Wagner (ORL) and Markkanen (CLE) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Stevens (CLE) steps on the baseline during his drive to the basket.
Schofield (ORL) applies a stayed forearm to Markkanen's (CLE) side and immediately removes his hand as marginal contact occurs.
Wagner (ORL) maintains verticality as he defends Markkanen's (CLE) driving shot attempt.
Brazdeikis (ORL) brushes Garland's (CLE) arm and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter during the rip-through.
Wagner (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Schofield (ORL) is already in Okoro's (CLE) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Dowtin (ORL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Garland (CLE) during rebounding.
Wagner (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Dowtin (ORL) brings his hand forward towards Garland's (CLE) front and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Schofield (ORL) commits a take foul on Windler (CLE).
Garland (CLE) and Dowtin (ORL) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Brazdeikis (ORL) commits a take foul on Garland (CLE).
Stevens (CLE) legally contests Okeke's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) commits a take foul on Windler (CLE).
